Prep installation media
Run alpine-setup. Do not create a regular user. Choose disk based install(or encrypted disk based)
Reboot
Log in as root
Install git
Clone repo and make alpinebootstrap executable
Run alpinebootstrap.sh with sh alpinebootstrap.sh
Create distrobox boxkit container AlpineTerminal
Unlock bitwarden export BW_SESSION=$(bw login --raw)
Chezmoi apply
Relog
Dotfiles, scripts and aliases are now available.
